OL,7,FThe other offences include two counts
OL,8,Fof sexual activity with a child by a
OL,9,Fperson in a position of trust, one
OL,10,Fcount of causing or inciting a child
OL,11,Fto engage in sexual activity,
OL,12,Fattempting to arrange the commission
OL,13,Fof a child sex offence, sexual
OL,14,Fcommunication with a child, possessing
OL,15,Findecent photographs of a child for
OL,16,Fshow, and the sexual assault of a
OL,17,Fchild under 13.
OL,19,FHe was found not guilty of one charge
OL,20,Fof sexual activity with a child.
