OL,7,FFor many years, Foden had been a
OL,8,Fteaching union leader and a local
OL,9,Fspokesman on educational issues.
OL,11,FITV Wales can reveal he previously
OL,12,Fraised concerns on television about
OL,13,Fteachers being suspended following
OL,14,Fcomplaints.
