OL,7,F"Due to the serious nature of the
OL,8,Fcase, arrangements are being made to
OL,9,Fcarry out an independent review in
OL,10,Faccordance with national child
OL,11,Fpractice review guidelines. The exact
OL,12,Fform of the review is currently being
OL,13,Fdetermined."
OL,15,FIn a statement, a National Education
OL,16,FUnion spokesperson said: "The offences
OL,17,Fcommitted by this individual are
OL,18,Fabhorrent and the NEU is appalled by
OL,19,Fthem. These were despicable and vile
OL,20,Facts, with lasting effects on his
OL,21,Fvictims.
