OL,7,F"No one should be above suspicion and
OL,8,Fwhen accusations or concerns are
OL,9,Fraised about an individual, from
OL,10,Fwhatever quarter or position of power,
OL,11,Fthey need to be fully investigated.
OL,13,F"Children and young people need to be
OL,14,Fconfident that they can speak out
OL,15,Fabout abuse, and school staff also
OL,16,Fneed to be confident that they will be
OL,17,Fgiven a serious hearing if they have
OL,18,Fconcerns.
