OL,7,F"The priority must always be the
OL,8,Fsafety of children and young people.
OL,9,FThis man's offences against children
OL,10,Fhave sickened and shocked the pupils,
OL,11,Fschool staff and the community in
OL,12,Fwhich he worked. Stringent and
OL,13,Fstrictly adhered to safeguarding
OL,14,Fmeasures in schools and colleges and
OL,15,Fby school governors and local
OL,16,Fauthorities must always be observed."
OL,18,FFoden is due to be sentenced at Mold
OL,19,FCrown Court on Monday, 1 July.
